snippet.title: [ASTRA: Knights of Veda] First Global Beta Coming Soon
snippet.description:
ASTRA : Knights of Veda participates in October Steam Next Fest 2023!
Be the first to experience an epic tale of cruelty and beauty.

[Steam Next Fest]
Come enjoy ASTRA : Knights of Veda on SNF!
9.OCT - 16.OCT 2023 (PT)

[Wishlist on Steam Now] 
Get a notification when the beta releases!
https://bit.ly/465qy8L 

[Follow our Official Channels] 
Pre-Registration Link : https://bit.ly/3rB3n7g
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/RCpbsE8UQz
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/knightsofveda.en/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/knightsofveda.global.official

#ASTRA #KnightsofVeda #SteamNextFest #SNF
